title: TezosPride
description:
Teia Community invites you to join our Tezos NFT Event #TezosPride from June 1st - June 30th to celebrate Pride Month!
Everyone is encouraged to participate with the theme of Pride and Community Support - whether you are a 2SLGBTQ+ artist or an Ally, lets bring some fun and colour to the ecosystem and support each other! Participants can mint on Tezos Marketplaces of their choice and use the tag TezosPride at mint time. No limit on number of submissions.
Let's support and uplift our 2SLGBTQ+ siblings in the ecosystem!
For more informations check this thread
